description: Welcome home to Vantage Point - a collection of 30 well appointed homes in the heart of South Boston outfitted in the finest finishes. Unit 305 boasts 1 large bedroom and 1 full bathroom which is dripping in quartz, designer lighting and plumbing fixtures. This South facing home has floor to ceiling windows allowing light to pour in. Open concept kitchen and living room lead out to your private deck waiting to host guests. The kitchen boasts two tone shaker cabinets, quartz counters and GE stainless steel appliances. Plethora of closet space is found throughout this unit. Wide plank oak flooring, central heat/AC. Ideal South Boston location! Close to everything - bars, restaurants, coffee shops, retail, Seaport, public transportation. Professionally manage and 1 GARAGE parking space included.
